description:
This free course, SEO 2016: Technical SEO Factors for Websites, is an excerpt from the premium course: WordPress SEO: 2016 SEO Training for WordPress Websites

This free course, SEO 2016: Technical SEO Factors for Websites, course is all about Technical SEO (Search Engine Optimization) factors. 

Technical SEO factors are the entry ticket for your website to enter into search engine ranking. If you haven't implemented this on your website yet, then your website is at a tactical disadvantage.

Each SEO factor is explained in the following ways:

> Why is that a SEO factor?

> Trend analysis for the SEO factor in the recent years

> Live example of how that SEO factor delivers results

> When and how to use these SEO factors?

All the lectures under these sections are produced, not just like that. They are all based on a keyword research from 10,000 keywords for top 30 searches across the year 2015. So they are all new and they apply 100% to 2016 and up.

This is a no fluff SEO course. Each and every lecture is prepared and polished with loads of rare information, SEO tutorial that produces results and examples or research data to justify those SEO factors.
title: SEO 2016: Technical SEO Factors Training for Websites
